name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI to Bunch of ML Models

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replaces 'AI', 'GenAI', and 'Artificial Intelligence' with 'A Bunch of ML Models' on web pages.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Chrome extension that replaces the combo of AI with "A Bunch of ML models", a nice jokey way to joke about AI ;) 

Just for laughs and fun and in good spirit of course
